snippet.title: Star Trooper for Commodore 64, published by Melbourne House
snippet.description:
This was our last ever published game before I went off to university. Another vertical shoot-em-up, ripping off just about every game I could think of. The difficulty of each level was a bit of a crap shoot. Wish I'd thought to arrange them in some sort of order.
The music on this was fantastic, but commissioned by Melbourne House and nothing whatsoever to do with me or Geddy Lee.
